# Build artifacts
/target/
fuzz/target/

# Rust backup files
**/*.rs.bk


# Working directories (all temporary/generated files must go here)
.work/

# Benchmark files (should be in .work/benchmarks/)
bench-corpus/
bench-results*.csv
bench-results*.md
LINKEDIN_BENCHMARK_REPORT.md
OPTIMIZATION_RECOMMENDATIONS.md

